Docker swarm
Global mode and replicated mode
docker service create --name mytest --mode global nginx
global:
deploy the service on each container in the worker node

replica mode:
randomly pick the worker node and deploy the container

Scale vs update:

to scale the replica value
both are same
docker service scale myservice=6
docker serbice update --replicas 5 myservice=7
